#, fuzzy
msgid "Next, if you need to access both mTLS and OIDC bearer security identities, consider enabling xref:security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc#combining-authentication-mechanisms[Inclusive authentication] with `quarkus.http.auth.inclusive=true`."
msgstr "Em seguida, caso precise acessar tanto as identidades de segurança de portador mTLS quanto as OIDC, considere habilitar xref:security-authentication-mechanisms.adoc#combining-authentication-mechanisms[a autenticação inclusiva] com `quarkus.http.auth.inclusive=true` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
